[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    199[0m:[38;5;10m[49m ### Issue 6 — NOTE: Mixed naive and timezone-aware ISO timestamps in forecast records
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    200[0m:[38;5;10m[49m 
