[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    202[0m:[38;5;10m[49m **File:** `chapter12.05-python-example.md`, `run_census_forecast_pipeline` and `compose_census`
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    203[0m:[38;5;10m[49m 
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    204[0m:[38;5;10m[49m `run_census_forecast_pipeline` strips the timezone from `snapshot_ts`:
