[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    232[0m:[38;5;10m[49m ### Issue 7 — NOTE: New admits during the horizon are never sampled for discharge
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    233[0m:[38;5;10m[49m 
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    234[0m:[38;5;10m[49m **Severity:** NOTE
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    235[0m:[38;5;10m[49m **File:** `chapter12.05-python-example.md`, `forecast_outflows` and `compose_census`
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    236[0m:[38;5;10m[49m 
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    237[0m:[38;5;10m[49m `forecast_outflows` runs the survival model only on the snapshot population (`state_records`):
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    238[0m:[38;5;10m[49m 
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    239[0m:[38;5;10m[49m ```python
