[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    257[0m:[38;5;10m[49m # (most new admits would not discharge same-day anyway). For
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    258[0m:[38;5;10m[49m # longer horizons (72+ hours), production samples synthetic
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    259[0m:[38;5;10m[49m # per-patient features for each new admit and runs the survival
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    260[0m:[38;5;10m[49m # model on them, or layers an aggregate count-based outflow on
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    261[0m:[38;5;10m[49m # top of the per-patient outflow.
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    262[0m:[38;5;10m[49m ```
