[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    268[0m:[38;5;10m[49m ### Issue 8 — NOTE: `current_census_by_unit` silently drops occupants of unknown units
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    269[0m:[38;5;10m[49m 
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    270[0m:[38;5;10m[49m **Severity:** NOTE
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    271[0m:[38;5;10m[49m **File:** `chapter12.05-python-example.md`, `current_census_by_unit` and `compose_census`
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    272[0m:[38;5;10m[49m 
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    273[0m:[38;5;10m[49m ```python
